						<summary>

						<p>This inscription records the gift of money (one <hi rend="italic">paḻañjalāgai</hi>) for burning a twilight lamp in the Āḷuḍaiyār temple by a brāhmaṇa named Saivapurandara-chakravartiṉ who had the <hi rend="italic">kāṇi</hi> right in the temple of Āḷuḍaiyār Vallāḷagaṇḍar at Īṅgaiyūr in Pūnduṟai-nāḍu.</p>						

